This project will use vagrant and puppet to 
install a complete Mozilla TBPL Server (https://wiki.mozilla.org/Tinderboxpushlog)
environment in a local VM.

---
INSTALL
---

1) Install the latest Virtualbox from http://www.virtualbox.org/ 

2) Run vagrant (http://vagrantup.com/) :

$ gem install vagrant
$ vagrant box add lucid64 http://files.vagrantup.com/lucid64.box
$ vagrant up

3) Add 33.33.33.11 to /etc/hosts:
33.33.33.11	tbpl

4) Enjoy your Mozilla TBPL environment!

dashboard:      http://tbpl

SSH into your VM:
$ vagrant ssh

---
KNOWN ISSUES
---

* depends on external buildbot/tinderbox/hgpushlog/bugzilla/etc
